{"tid":1925171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最後通牒！不回支那為CBA效力就終身停賽封殺　林書豪將面臨抉擇","createTime":"2020-03-14T07:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T08:44:51.000Z","uid":32511,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"805e8babb01126628b4ca6f8feb43535f93cd997","tid":1925171,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"NBA決定停賽後，另一焦點又回到中國CBA是否復賽，結果目前傳出4月初將重新展開賽事，並且各球隊要求經紀人要把各隊外援找回去，其中也包括華裔球星林書豪，他是否回歸北京首鋼令人關注。<br />\n <br />\n林書豪日前在台灣參加屏東燈會，也跟母親一起過婦女節，他究竟是否會回到中國打球，還是要面對武漢病毒威脅，日前他也在推特寫下：「我真的很害怕。」<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n不過中國球隊要求經紀人要讓球員歸隊，否則將祭出終身禁賽令，林書豪是否會放棄CBA球季，他必須要做出抉擇。"},{"pid":"91734486d4377ef5d9f895dbfa99066413c87da7","tid":1925171,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"唔番去你就係歧視支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bd2e7469b1e970e3600a11ff425e5797d62bc7","tid":1925171,"uid":315299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41372ce2cabefa8f90ec0cd41ae0a4eda380b284","tid":1925171,"uid":192824,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"算唔算回力標？ 早2.日先話美國叫武漢肺炎係岐視<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b173b6ab4edde2e9775e48b4892977a29b8b06","tid":1925171,"uid":140793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"報應真係話嚟就嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1b2eb7aca361c255e08aaaacd453f69fe149f0","tid":1925171,"uid":67208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"大把地方打波啦  啲錢都得下半世"},{"pid":"368577a8ea1c945f933fd31a52b900dd6b34e000","tid":1925171,"uid":125623,"like":0,"dislike"